{"type": "article", "id": 58072, "title": "皮卡丘 “代言” OPPO，Google 推出营销小程序 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-11-07T04:15:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 701, "name": "商业"}, {"id": 4489, "name": "代言"}, {"id": 3688, "name": "OPPO"}, {"id": 148, "name": "谷歌"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181107111405l7C3o0QrgXcV4DUM.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"PfTB\">明星已经不够用了，<b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4303370195669554?\" rel=\"nofollow\">OPPO 的新代言人找上了皮卡丘</a>，</b>它成为 OPPO 超级闪充电力大使。并且和精灵宝可梦进行合作，推出了皮卡丘定制版闪充移动电源、保护壳，NFC 主题卡等周边。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107111858Uyu4xD6qRwXsSIg3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107111750az05yVBt6sYQIGX4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"iw6P\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4303450407823625?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>王老吉推出 190 周年纪念款特别包装，</b></a>新包装换成了品牌代言人刘昊然和周冬雨的 Q 版萌趣形象。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018110711211041pXcHQS7axuLkGT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.165333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107112129sX8GdIPKJDtAlxUW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.165957\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107112017VE8ZhwmUOJB4pXkW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.163807\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107111953q7E1JOBNeUiHRc5p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.165333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p line=\"VoXV\"><b>天猫<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUyMzkyNjk4OQ==&amp;mid=2247484164&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1d463a21a823755408153fd187d01603&amp;chksm=fa346fa6cd43e6b0272777986e82d239105dd7e856814c62fbbb6ebc9cede2a062ae1def8cbc&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1106mkInBnJIlnofbMsf4iN6&amp;key=9890e69e3fe7c346056b1224d9e8eba4d284c0dae8c86080f16c1ede91176fcc9ae8febb0c16d1da6bf306e80990e9570600cb0eef520c0c2fb46ee5ea5042aeb3c1190f81622b8f23c2bc10972acdbd&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=IwMqXt28r%2FlZKT9GZcOHAs9K2tFFEI8rQ7Ga6uFEcPv8cSFqjY5q8bFPrXbXjBCR\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">发布“天猫双 11 十周年回忆商店”，</a></b>列举了每一年热点事件之后，发生在淘宝上的购物变化。“洪荒之力”成为当年流行语时候，傅园慧表情包在淘宝上相关周边热销了 2 万件。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107112205fGQzuiNrlvSt5hIw.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"7.382667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"xlFx\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4303297986664154?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>华为 Mate20 上线新广告，</b></a>片中一群不同时空的游戏人物控诉手机丢帧、卡顿、渣性能，最终在游戏中”挂掉”，从而表示使用华为 Mate20 能够提升游戏体验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s0785dbizx7\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"zdgv\"><a href=\"https://jiazhang.qq.com/jz/a20181101czshpt/index.html?wx_aid=1689975128&amp;tid=1689975131&amp;gdt_vid=wx0xbcpfloomu3sc00&amp;wx_traceid=wx0xbcpfloomu3sc00&amp;ADTAG=tgi.wx.share.message\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>腾讯投放了一个沉浸式的 H5，</b></a>故事围绕孩子沉迷游戏的主题展开，爸爸向家庭成员们寻求建议时，彼此用视频通话和表情包发表了自己的看法（并不管用），最终引出推荐使用“腾讯成长守护平台”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107112553AhGtQij6spg9WMFN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"A9JP\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4302935766689903?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">飘柔代言人王俊凯出演广告片“爱乐之城，遇上飘柔”。</a>全片以舞蹈来推进情节，没有加旁白和台词。指导拍摄的导演 Mark Kudsi 曾获得格莱美奖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p078467aj3u\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"9tE9\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjg4Mzg5ODA0MA==&amp;mid=2656249613&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e94a859f05b110b85464b0ebed8c3dbe&amp;chksm=987cbadaaf0b33ccf47d78d1dc68957f9376b134189bee76f34ede64a205fab8d37e1a8e4fb5&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=110735huxVv9K5KZrQoWWH1x&amp;key=84e1ab98e194bf2d7ff0dfa49f103ce429de06c4be531e54a929cf946f21e815874e7108f2746f3dcae414acc6a0c8f9d736e6c94a7afbe1a11c282755d06a02efda5687e147b5309fa86595cf0e7af0&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=mLTrdDbC%2B%2B4jFMtJdiYsSuX36OyOKxDJwnVXN%2FrGsAGlPyWnXcURBXISP%2Fp5iQrl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>星巴克昨天上线了今年的圣诞主题红杯，</b></a>以红、绿、白为设计主线，杯身还设计有咖啡树、五角星等复古纹理图案。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107112809mVSFNJEzBPRArgQT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.949000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"79PP\">可口可乐今年的圣诞卡车之旅要开始了，<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=12&amp;v=HKRm1K8OxPQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>零度可乐将成为这一趟旅程的主角。</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107112833epXB5SMCAkd4cUo8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.533333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"vp8H\">雀巢中国（集团）日前经过比稿，<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4NzMwNDQxMQ==&amp;mid=2650383167&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e6da13607a097227a127c2eceb2f5252&amp;chksm=8836728bbf41fb9d078b5aa8dd5c4f6a32b00c0a4796c986bc27ccceb8e5170df133a35be72d&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1107rgHL5RjfugajTDRTzHUK&amp;key=b97634afb8bc8a87190f72da39a6a6c704a0b30687fd7be6adc221fb09dff1522364a9bbaae197fadc75cbdb2c8664de099a018fc1237063db9050d58f2f20cfbe34ce6a4353f460268200b5d66e7c00&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=mLTrdDbC%2B%2B4jFMtJdiYsSuX36OyOKxDJwnVXN%2FrGsAGlPyWnXcURBXISP%2Fp5iQrl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>将旗下所有品牌的媒介购买业务统一委任给群邑旗下的传立媒体（ Mindshare ）。</b></a>传立媒体会负责其中的雀巢品牌和惠氏营养品两大块的媒介策划业务。预计雀巢总媒介花费应该在 10 亿- 15 亿人民币之间。</p><p line=\"LpG9\">Google 推出一款营销教程小程序“谷歌成长指南”。这是一款面向营销人员的教程工具，包含营销、运营、数据分析等多个微型免费课程，每一个课程围绕一个主题展开。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181107112914mFKSRAMJVUW4oEl9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.825926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"prmM\"><a href=\"https://www.managingmadrid.com/2018/11/6/18066664/real-madrid-to-sign-new-record-breaking-adidas-deal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>阿迪达斯将以每年 1.1 亿欧元的价格继续签约皇马赞助，</b></a>是现在价格的两倍多，创下新纪录。这一赞助会持续 10 年，据说耐克、安德玛都感兴趣，不过都开不出阿迪达斯这样的高价。</p><p line=\"prmM\" class=\"\"><br></p><p line=\"prmM\" class=\"\">题图来自：微博@OPPO</p>"}